        <div style="width:34px;height:3px;background:#0E4A7C;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:16px;"></div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.25;">The strictest quality, at every site</div>
